{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_07_02",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 2話 お父さんに見せたくて",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、{user}さん\n芽衣、あのウエディングドレス……着てみたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}-san.\nMei wants to try on that… wedding dress!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣？　急にどうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei? What's gotten into you all of a sudden?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "えっとね、この間お父さんのお見舞いに行ったんだけど\nお父さんね、けろっとしてたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I visited Dad at the hospital the other day.\nHe was being all nonchalant‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.4
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、「うーん、一人で病院にいると\n寂しくて元気が出ないなー」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "saying stuff like‚ \"Hmm‚ being alone at the hospital is\nkinda lonely and get me down.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.1039442657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "「可愛い娘の花嫁姿を見たら元気が出るんだけどなー」\nなんて冗談ぽく言ってたんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"But if I saw my cute daughter in a bridal gown‚ it might cheer me up.\"\nHe said it jokingly‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "お父さんね、本当に、ちょっと寂しそうだったんだ\nいつもよりちっちゃく見えた気がして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but he really did seem a bit lonely.\nHe looked smaller than usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "最近忙しくて、実家に帰れてなかったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been busy lately and haven't been able to go home‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9666643779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.7999977112
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "お父さん、ずっと芽衣のこと見守って\n応援してくれてたから……たまには親孝行したいなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and since Dad's always been watching over me and supporting me…\nI thought I'd do something nice for him once in a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1666643779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.3666643779
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "それにほら！　今、雨で濡れちゃってるでしょ？\n着替えるのにちょうどいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus‚ look! We're all wet from the rain‚ aren't we?\nWouldn't it be perfect to change into it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……いや、やめておこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ let's not do that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.7666684468
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "……ダメ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Really?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "着替えるだけじゃなくてちゃんと体を温めた方がいい\n改めて時間を作ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not just about changing clothes; it's better to warm up properly.\nLet's reschedule and make time for it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.8000010172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.1333320617
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "それって……また一緒に来てくれるってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Does that mean… you'll come with me again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1333320617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.066665395
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣がお父さんのことを本当に大事に想ってるのが\n分かったからな。俺も付き合うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand how much you care about\nyour dad. I'll come along.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.2666676838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.0999987284
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "やったー！　{user}さん、大好き！\nよーし、まずは早く事務所に戻らないと！　ゴーゴー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay! I love you‚ {user}-san!\nAlright‚ first‚ we need to hurry back to the office! Let's go‚ let's go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.004359868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "こらこら、背中を押すんじゃない……まったく\nとりあえずタクシーを呼んで来るよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey now‚ don't push me… honestly.\nLet's call a taxi first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.0000010172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few day later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.3655304628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.4333343505
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.4333343505
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "はい、これ！　こないだの撮影スタジオから\nパンフレットをもらってきたんだー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here it is! I got this flyer from the photo studio\nthe other day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.6666676838,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 266.67556760000366,
          "startTime": 117.5666676838
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いつの間にこんなものを……。というか\n俺は日を改めさえすれば良かったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When did you… and I think\nwe can reschedule it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.9000010172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.3333254496
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣も最初はそう思ってたんだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At first‚ Mei thought the same thing too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.3333254496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.8666676838
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "このことを優ちゃんに話したら、「せっかく貴重な\n機会なんやし、しっかり準備せんと！」って言われて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But when I told Yu-chan about it‚ she said‚\n\"It's a precious opportunity‚ so you better prepare properly!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.7333343505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "後はね、打ち合わせでいきなり資料をばーんと見せて\n逃げ場をなくすのも優ちゃんの作戦！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ during the meeting‚ she suddenly showed me\nthe materials to corner me. It's all Yu-chan's strategy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.6666676838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.8333254496
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "優らしいにも程があるな……\nまぁ、芽衣がお父さんを喜ばせたい気持ちは分かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's so like Yu…\nWell‚ I understand that you want to make your dad happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.9000010172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.0999921162
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
